import {Component, OnInit} from '@angular/core'; import {FormControl, FormGroup} from "@angular/forms"; @Component({ selector: 'app-carros', templateUrl: './carros.component.html', styleUrls: ['./carros.component.css'] }) export class CarrosComponent implements OnInit { formulario: any; tituloFormulario: string = "Formulario de Carros"; constructor() { } ngOnInit() { this.formulario = new FormGroup({ marca: new FormControl(null), modelo: new FormControl(null), estacionado: new FormControl(null), dataEntrada: new FormControl(null), dataSaida: new FormControl(null), cliente: new FormControl(null) }) } }
{{tituloFormulario}}
